{"tid":2500131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國通過“2021年戰略競爭法案” 中國強烈反對：搬起石頭砸腳","createTime":"2021-04-22T11:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T11:51:29.000Z","uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f05d9ef9662997335a1253964f155fbacb0ba6","tid":2500131,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:45:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">全國人大外事委員會發言人就美國國會參議院外委會通過&ldquo;2021年戰略競爭法案&rdquo;發表談話</span></strong><br />\n來源：新華網<br />\n<br />\n2021-04-22 16:59<br />\n<br />\n新華社北京4月22日電4月22日，<span class=\"red\">針對美國國會參議院外委會審議通過&ldquo;2021年戰略競爭法案&rdquo;</span>，全國人大外事委員會發言人尤文澤表示，<span class=\"red\">該法案充斥冷戰思維和意識形態偏見，肆意曲解、誣衊抹黑中國發展戰略和內外政策，粗暴干涉中國內政，用心險惡，損人害己，我們對此表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。<br />\n</span><br />\n發言人指出，在百年變局和世紀疫情交織疊加，世界進入動盪變革期，不穩定性不確定性顯著上升的大背景下，該法案蓄意製造意識形態對抗，搞零和博弈，既不符合時代潮流，也不利於促進世界的和平、穩定與發展，注定沒有出路。中國堅持真正的多邊主義，堅定維護以聯合國為核心的國際體系，堅定維護以國際法為基礎的國際秩序，堅定維護以世界貿易組織為核心的多邊貿易體制，主張世界各國平等相待，互尊互信，同舟共濟，共克時艱。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指出，台灣問題事關中國的國家主權和領土完整，涉及中國的核心利益。法案相關涉台條款嚴重違反一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報規定，向&ldquo;台獨&rdquo;勢力發出嚴重錯誤信號。一個中國原則是中國的紅線，我們堅決反對任何形式的美台官方往來。涉疆、涉港問題純屬中國內政，不容任何外國干涉。<br />\n<br />\n發言人強調，中美即便在某些領域存在競爭，也應該是公平公正、遵守規則的良性、有序競爭。中國一貫主張構建不衝突不對抗、相互尊重、合作共贏的中美關係，同時堅定捍衛國家主權、安全和發展利益。我們強烈敦促美國國會客觀理性看待中國發展，切實尊重中國主權和領土完整，停止插手中國內政，停止審議推進該法案。<br />\n<br />\n舉報我也說兩句責編：任鑫恚"},{"pid":"058e6763d8a62fe1b027d889ecb3b18632850d7c","tid":2500131,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:46:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">「2021年戰略競爭法案」納友我條款 外交部：誠摯歡迎與感謝</span></strong><br />\n新頭殼newtalk | 謝莉慧 綜合報導<br />\n發布 2021.04.22 | 12:15<br />\n     <br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/367/5e44c744ea28f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F367%2F5e44c744ea28f.JPG&h=20080f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外交部發言人歐江安。   圖：林朝億/攝（資料照片）<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦參議院外交委員會於美東時間21日審議並通過「2021年戰略競爭法案」（Strategic Competition Act of 2021）。該法案由參院外交委員會主席孟南德茲（Robert Menendez, D-NJ）及共和黨首席議員芮胥（Jim Risch, R-ID）共同提出，是參院民主、共和兩黨共同制定對中戰略方針的第一項重大法案，<span class=\"red\">其中也納入多項友我條文，內容涵蓋台美安全、經濟、政治等各層面的夥伴關係，外交部今（22）天對此表達誠摯歡迎與感謝。 </span><br />\n<br />\n外交部指出，該法案內容包括：重申美對台承諾、支持台灣自我防衛能力並嚇阻中國武力進犯、透過重啟「貿易暨投資架構協定」（TIFA)及洽簽自由貿易協定（FTA)等方式強化雙邊經貿關係、支持台灣國際參與、協助因應中國銳實力攻擊，以及改善對台灣政府待遇。該法案也納入多項美國會審議中的友我法案，包括：深化台美在語言及專業領域實質交流合作的「台灣學人法案」（Taiwan Fellowship Act），以及要求不得限制台灣政府代表或軍人在執行公務時展示具主權象徵的國旗或軍事徽章的「2021年承諾再保證法案」（Reassurance On Commitments Act of 2021, ROC Act）等。 <br />\n<br />\n外交部感謝美國國會長期以來不斷透過立法等方式，積極推動深化台美關係，彰顯美國會不分黨派對台灣的一致支持。近年來台美關係的深化各界有目共睹，美國拜登政府上任後，也持續不斷以具體行動展現對台美關係的重視與支持。外交部將持續關注該法案的後續審議情形，並與美國國會友人及行政部門保持密切聯繫，以持續深化台美全方位合作夥伴關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-22/567132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-04-22%2F567132&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrdqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=24bb7d1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-22/567132</a>"},{"pid":"454f2a99a701ba9adcfe93e5afe7077b358a2d24","tid":2500131,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20201506_PO_%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD.png&amp;h=e665866f&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"4d4ee84fdb5f01f93e5928af18a71912c4c562cb","tid":2500131,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"澳州撚完到美國撚中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab9e5c0224c00765b5b5634ace5151f7fd5aa78","tid":2500131,"uid":383539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"比啲本是<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb2a18e2f76dafc493d8c81f4cda1487d9d4271","tid":2500131,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"454f2a99a701ba9adcfe93e5afe7077b358a2d24","tid":2500131,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20201506_PO_%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD.png&amp;h=e665866f&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b7c3348dd23d4abf2f095c87b3eb500bbc7f21","tid":2500131,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美國國會推動重大抗中法案 內容重點一次看</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2021/04/22 14:37<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者徐薇婷華盛頓21日專電）對抗中國威權野心在美國已成跨黨派議題，為確保美國未來數十年有能力與中國全方位競爭，兩黨資深議員近日合力催生美國近年首部重大抗中法案，今天順利通過參議院外委會。<br />\n<br />\n●助美企撤出中國分散供應鏈 提「一帶一路」因應方案<br />\n<br />\n●每年挹注3億美元 對抗中共全球惡意影響力<br />\n<br />\n●對抗數位威權 籲與台日歐五眼簽數位貿易協定<br />\n<br />\n●美方應首重印太 反制中國軍事擴張、對台野心<br />\n<br />\n●台灣為美國印太戰略重要一環 應強化夥伴關係<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202104220019.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202104220019.aspx&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrdqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=10de61a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202104220019.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"e5c299416343eea0c71c6b63a3e65ea47ddc3ab4","tid":2500131,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb2a18e2f76dafc493d8c81f4cda1487d9d4271","tid":2500131,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"454f2a99a701ba9adcfe93e5afe7077b358a2d24","tid":2500131,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20201506_PO_%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD.png&amp;h=e665866f&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da24d27867c3c943023cfe4322898e03df475b92","tid":2500131,"uid":132572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"石頭 腳<br />\n笑左差唔多兩年<br />\n仲係石頭 腳"},{"pid":"5ae2d9fde37f9d3ea8502dccd44ba3ec50d1ff11","tid":2500131,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d4ee84fdb5f01f93e5928af18a71912c4c562cb","tid":2500131,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"澳州撚完到美國撚中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"中國的石頭大漲價"},{"pid":"e15f4630c3dcff25885430419cee99985e577619","tid":2500131,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"同我一齊嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n石頭腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n石頭腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n石頭腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n石頭腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n石頭腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n石頭腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}